al constituency)|Tanah Merah]] || Ikmal Hisham Abdul Aziz || bgcolor=\"{{Malaysian United Indigenous Party/meta/shading}}\" | ||PPBM\n|-\n| P028 || [[Pasir Puteh (federal constituency)|Pasir Puteh]] || Nik Muhammad Zawawi Salleh || bgcolor=\"{{Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PAS\n|- \n| P029 || [[Machang (federal constituency)|Machang]] || Ahmad Jazlan Yaakub || bgcolor=\"{{United Malays National Organisation/meta/shading}}\"| ||UMNO\n|-\n| P030 || [[Jeli (federal constituency)|Jeli]] || [[Mustapa Mohamed]] || bgcolor=\"{{Malaysian United Indigenous Party/meta/shading}}\" | ||PPBM\n|-\n| P031 || [[Kuala Krai (federal constituency)|Kuala Krai]] || Abdul Latiff Abdul Rahman || bgcolor=\"{{Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PAS\n|- \n| P032 || [[Gua Musang (federal constituency)|Gua Musang]] || [[Tengku Razaleigh Hamzah]] || bgcolor=\"{{United Malays National Organisation/meta/shading}}\"| ||UMNO\n|-\n|rowspan=8| {{Flag|Terengganu}} || P033 || [[Besut (federal constituency)|Besut]] || [[Idris Jusoh]] || bgcolor=\"{{United Malays National Organisation/meta/shading}}\"| ||UMNO\n|-\n| P034 || [[Setiu (federal constituency)|Setiu]] || Shaharizukirnain Abd. Kadir || bgcolor=\"{{Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PAS\n|- \n| P035 || [[Kuala Nerus (federal constituency)|Kuala Nerus]] || Mohd. Khairuddin Aman Razali || bgcolor=\"{{Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PAS\n|- \n| P036 || [[Kuala Terengganu (federal constituency)|Kuala Terengganu]] || Ahmad Amzad Mohamed Hashim || bgcolor=\"{{Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PAS\n|- \n| P037 || [[Marang (federal constituency)|Marang]] || [[Abdul Hadi Awang]] || bgcolor=\"{{Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PAS\n|- \n| P038 || [[Hulu Terengganu (federal constituency)|Hulu Terengganu]] || [[Rosol Wahid]] || bgcolor=\"{{Malaysian United Indigenous Party/meta/shading}}\" | ||PPBM\n|-\n| P039 || [[Dungun (federal constituency)|Dungun]] || Wan Hassan Moh