g (federal constituency)|Sipitang]] || [[Yamani Hafez Musa]] || bgcolor=\"{{Malaysian United Indigenous Party/meta/shading}}\" | ||PPBM\n|-\n| P179 || [[Ranau (federal constituency)|Ranau]] || [[Jonathan Yasin]] || bgcolor=\"{{Independent (politician)/meta/color}}\"| ||IND\n|-\n| P180 || [[Keningau (federal constituency)|Keningau]] || [[Jeffrey Kitingan]] || bgcolor=\"{{Homeland Solidarity Party/meta/shading}}\"| || STAR\n|-\n| P182 || [[Pensiangan (federal constituency)|Pensiangan]] || [[Arthur Joseph Kurup]] || bgcolor=\"{{Parti Bersatu Rakyat Sabah/meta/shading}}\"| || PBRS\n|-\n| P183 || [[Beluran (federal constituency)|Beluran]] || [[Ronald Kiandee]] || bgcolor=\"{{Malaysian United Indigenous Party/meta/shading}}\" | ||PPBM\n|-\n| P184 || [[Libaran (federal constituency)|Libaran]] || [[Zakaria Edris]] || bgcolor=\"{{Malaysian United Indigenous Party/meta/shading}}\" | ||PPBM\n|-\n| P187 || [[Kinabatangan (federal constituency)|Kinabatangan]] || [[Bung Moktar Radin]] || bgcolor=\"{{United Malays National Organisation/meta/shading}}\"| ||UMNO\n|-\n| rowspan=\"20\" | {{Flag|Sarawak}} || P193 || [[Santubong (federal constituency)|Santubong]] || [[Wan Junaidi Tuanku Jaafar]] || bgcolor=\"{{United Bumiputera Heritage Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||[[United Bumiputera Heritage Party|PBB]]\n|-\n| P194 || [[Petra Jaya (federal constituency)|Petra Jaya]] || [[Fadillah Yusof]] || bgcolor=\"{{United Bumiputera Heritage Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PBB\n|-\n| P197 || [[Kota Samarahan (federal constituency)|Kota Samarahan]] || [[Rubiah Wang]] || bgcolor=\"{{United Bumiputera Heritage Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||PBB\n|-\n| P198 || [[Puncak Borneo (federal constituency)|Puncak Borneo]] || [[Willie Mongin]] || bgcolor=\"{{Independent (politician)/meta/color}}\"| ||IND\n|-\n| P199 || [[Serian (federal constituency)|Serian]] || [[Richard Riot Jaem]] || bgcolor=\"{{Sarawak United Peoples' Party/meta/shading}}\"| ||[[Sarawak United Peoples' Party|SUPP]]\n|-\n| P200 || [[Batang Sadong (federa